---
title: Easy Yoghurt Chicken & Couscous Salad with Roasted Almonds
description: There’s nothing better than chicken that’s juicy on the inside and wonderfully charred with mild spices and yoghurt on the outside. That’s how we’re preparing our protein tonight, plus add a vibrant couscous salad to double down on all that flavour.
